•	What is the total revenue per customer?
Code: SELECT c.CustomerID, Name, sum(Revenue) as Revenue
FROM customers as c
JOIN orders as o ON c.CustomerID = o.CustomerID
group by c.CustomerID, Name
order by sum(Revenue) desc

•	What is the total revenue per product?
Code: SELECT Product, SUM(UnitsSold) AS "Units Sold", SUM(Revenue) AS "Revenue"
FROM orders
GROUP BY Product
ORDER BY SUM(Revenue) DESC

•	what is the monthly orders per product?
Code: SELECT Product, MONTH(Date) as Month, (COUNT(OrderID)) AS Orders
FROM orders
GROUP BY Product, Date
ORDER BY MONTH(Date) ASC

Used: SELECT, FROM, JOIN, GROUP BY, ORDER BY, SUM, COUNT, string function time MONTH. 
